data.description: Nestled on Niles Avenue in St. Joseph, this inviting residence presents an ideal haven with its desirable features. Boasting three bedrooms and two bathrooms, this home effortlessly blends comfort and functionality. The detached garage offers convenient parking and storage options, while the fenced-in backyard provides a private oasis for relaxation and entertaining. With a versatile unfinished basement, there's ample potential to customize and expand the living space to suit your unique needs and preferences. Imagine the possibilities for a personalized home office, gym, or recreation area. The thoughtful layout make this house a perfect canvas for your dream home. Embrace the warmth of a welcoming community while enjoying the convenience of near the convenience of nearby amenities!
